quote: Cooperation is the thorough conviction that nobody can get there unless everybody gets there.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf433873b8>

quote: The strength of the team is each individual member. The strength of each member is the team.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf43380fb8>

quote: Talent wins games, but teamwork wins championships.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf4339c128>

quote: Problems can become opportunities when the right people come together.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf43397948>

quote: When there is teamwork and collaboration, wonderful things can be achieved.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf43392588>

quote: When we strive to become better than we are, everything around us becomes better, too.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf433ac320>

quote: Inspiration exists, but it has to find us working.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf433a7e60>

quote: Keep your face always toward the sunshine—and shadows will fall behind you.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf433a1240>

quote: Light tomorrow with today.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf433b9e30>

quote: Learn from yesterday, live for today, hope for tomorrow.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf433b4890>

quote: Waste no more time arguing what a good person should be. Be one.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf433cf280>

quote: What we know matters but who we are matters more.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf433ca6e0>

quote: Be more concerned with your character than your reputation, because your character is what you really are, while your reputation is merely what others think you are.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf433c5280>

quote: The truth of your character is expressed through the choice of your actions.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf433df8d8>

quote: Character may be manifested in the great moments, but it is made in the small ones.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf433db0f8>

quote: The capacity to care is the thing which gives life its deepest significance.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf433d6878>

quote: Taking care is one way to show your love. Another way is letting people take good care of you when you need it.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf433d1cd8>

quote: I cannot do all the good that the world needs. But the world needs all the good that I can do.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf4342cbd8>

quote: Unless someone like you cares a whole awful lot, nothing is going to get better. It's not.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf434282b8>

quote: Kindness can transform someone’s dark moment with a blaze of light. You’ll never know how much your caring matters. Make a difference.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf43422e58>

quote: Confidence comes not from always being right, but from not fearing to be wrong.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf4344c3c0>

quote: Every small positive change we make in ourselves repays us in confidence in the future.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf43447b40>

quote: Never dull your shine for somebody else.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf43442140>

quote: You have no control over other people's taste, so focus on staying true to your own.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf4345d7b0>

quote: What lies behind you and what lies in front of you pales in comparison to what lies inside you.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf43459110>

quote: If you see something beautiful in someone, speak it!
author: <Author:0x00007fbf434546b0>

quote: Beauty is not in the face; beauty is a light in the heart.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf4347fc98>

quote: I can't think of any better representation of beauty than someone who is unafraid to be herself.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf4347a518>

quote: The sign of a beautiful person is that they always see beauty in others.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf434755b8>

quote: Beauty begins the moment you decide to be yourself.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf43470f18>

quote: Be good for something while you live and it is in your power.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf4349c780>

quote: As we work to create light for others, we naturally light our own way.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf43497780>

quote: Charity, like the sun, brightens every object on which it shines.
author: <Author:0x00007fbf43491740>
